	BITFILES LABORATORY

This is a simple program to convert mp4 files to mp3.
It also embeds a thumbnail to the mp3 file.


	Procedure

1. Get an mp4 file.
2. Extract a thumbnail from position x in the mp4.
3. Save the thumnail.
4. Extract the mp3 from the mp4
5. Embed the thumbnail into the mp3 and save it.


	Advanced.
 Repeat the above for all files in a folder.

